response.overview: Fiona is Australia's true Queen of Comedy with sold out seasons across the globe at Edinburgh Hong Kong Montreal and of course right across our wide brown land. Fiona\'s army of fans have voted her in shows in droves across more than a decade of her live shows. She fearlessly presents unvarnished hilarious honesty swiping through the grit of life - nothing is sacred! This DVD features Fiona\'s greatest hits of comedy a huge selection of her most popular stories and jokes. Guaranteed to leave audiences rolling around in stitches on the couch Fiona O\'Loughlin Greatest Hits is a must see for fans who have seen her perform before or total newcomers to her work - a unique opportunity to see the very best of Fiona O\'Loughlin in one sitting!
response.title: Fiona O'Loughlin's Greatest Hits
